Global Rechargeable Ultrasonic Oral Irrigator Market Insights
Rechargeable Ultrasonic Oral Irrigator Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Rechargeable Ultrasonic Oral Irrigator Market Overview
The global rechargeable ultrasonic oral irrigator market is experiencing significant growth, driven by increasing awareness about oral hygiene and advancements in dental care technology. With a market value of USD 3.8 billion in 2023, the industry is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.2% over the forecast period, reaching USD 6.2 billion by 2030. This growth can be attributed to rising consumer preference for convenient, effective, and eco-friendly dental care solutions. North America and Europe dominate the market, owing to high consumer awareness and technological innovations in oral care devices.

